comments: Bridges (CHA) briefly places his hand on Gobert's (MIN) right side and then immediately slides it off. The contact that occurs is marginal.
Washington (CHA) aligns along Edwards' (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs as the two players come together during the drive.
Edwards (MIN) does not step out of bounds during his dribble along the sideline.
Ball (CHA) brings his arm down and avoids making contact with McDaniels' (MIN) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Rozier (CHA) reaches for the ball and makes contact with McDaniels' (MIN) arm after he has gathered.
Washington (CHA) reaches for the ball and makes contact with Gobert's (MIN) right arm, affecting his ability to secure the rebound.
Gobert (MIN) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Washington (CHA) firms up over his right leg and marginal contact occurs as Alexander-Walker (MIN) defends over the pick.
Rozier (CHA) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes more than two steps before releasing his shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) and Gobert (MIN) briefly come together while running toward the paint and the contact is marginal.
Washington (CHA) extends his arms into Gobert (MIN) and dislodges him from his legally obtained rebounding position.

While a CHA foul is warranted on Alexander-Walker's (MIN) shot attempt, the call should have been called on Washington (CHA) for jumping A to B into Alexander-Walker during his shot attempt and not Miller (CHA), who cleanly dislodges the ball.
Gobert (MIN) brings his hand toward the ball and marginal brush contact occurs with Washington's (CHA) arm.
Anderson (MIN) reaches for the ball and makes contact with Ball's (CHA) arm after his gather, which causes him to lose control of the ball.
McDaniels (MIN) releases the ball prior to his right foot coming down out of bounds.
Washington (CHA) turns his body into Edwards (MIN) and contact occurs that affects Edwards' driving shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) absorbs the marginal contact with Ball (CHA) prior to bringing his left hand to the ball and deflecting it away during Ball's dribble drive.
Ball (CHA) pins the ball to his body, which is considered a gather, and then resumes his dribble.
From available angles, it does not appear that Ball's (CHA) heel comes down on the sideline before his shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) makes contact to Ball's (CHA) right arm with his left hand during his upward shooting motion.
Towns (MIN) firms up in Rozier's (CHA) path and does not deliver any illegal contact when setting the pick.
Rozier (CHA) reaches across Towns (MIN) and causes contact with his arm as he attempts to gather the ball.
Black (CHA) makes contact to Towns' (MIN) arm during his shooting motion.
McDaniels (MIN) commits a take foul on Black (CHA). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Gobert (MIN) grabs and pulls Bridges' (CHA) jersey away from his body, which affects his ability to defend the inbound pass.
Bridges (CHA) legally contests Towns' (MIN) perimeter jump shot attempt.
